[I] A LAPACK marshalling library

[T] hipSOLVER is a LAPACK marshalling library, with multiple supported
[T] backends. It sits between the application and a 'worker' LAPACK library,
[T] marshalling inputs into the backend library and marshalling results back to
[T] the application.

[U] https://github.com/ROCm/hipSOLVER

